smug.py 0.1
--------
Simple console based music player for MacOS X

smug acts as a wrapper around afplay and afinfo to play music. Since it
uses core audio, its very lightweight and supports a variety of file formats.

Installation:
-------------
1. make it executable: chmod +x smug.py
2. add smug folder to your path: export PATH=${PATH}:`pwd`
    (alternatively put smug.py in your /bin)

Usage:
------
navigate to folder with music
$ smug.py

recursively find and play all music in folder
$ smug.py -r

for party mode (shuffle songs)
$ smug.py -s

Keyboard Shortcuts:
-------------------
j/k, n/p - next/previous song
s - jump to random song
r - rewind song
l - toggle loop song
/ - jump to song (fuzzy search)
spacebar - toggle play/pause
q - quit

